videoSnippet.title: Modern Chess Brilliancy || Fischer vs Tal || Leipzig Olympiad (1960)
videoSnippet.description:
Watch Fischer Beat Tal for the First time ever here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W8Fpr_9-PxA

Have a great day :)

Robert James Fischer vs Mikhail Tal
"French Drawings" (game of the day Oct-15-2007)
Leipzig Olympiad Final-A (1960), Leipzig GDR, rd 5, Nov-01
French Defense: Winawer. Retreat Variation Armenian Line (C18)
